
<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'Home | Children\'s Vision Organization' }) %>

<main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 lg:flex lg:gap-12">
    
    <div class="lg:w-3/5">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1488521787991-ed7bbaae773c?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000" alt="Children" class="w-full rounded shadow-sm mb-6">
        
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase">SUPPORT INDIA'S CHILDREN IN NEED</h1>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
            <p>Bridge of Hopes, also known as Save the Children, is a leading independent child rights NGO in India. Since our inception, we have reached over 14 million children across the country.</p>
            <p>Your contribution helps us reach the most marginalized children, ensuring they have access to quality education, life-saving healthcare, and protection from all forms of violence and exploitation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 uppercase border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-3">Our Commitment</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We work on the ground every day and in times of crisis. Our programs are designed to address the unique challenges faced by children in India, from malnutrition to child labor.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:w-2/5 mt-8 lg:mt-0">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-2xl border border-gray-100 sticky top-6">
            
            <div class="flex w-full mb-6 border rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                <button type="button" id="giveOnceBtn" onclick="toggleDonationType('once')" class="flex-1 py-3 bg-[#4db748] text-white font-bold transition-colors">
                    Give Once
                </button>
                <button type="button" id="giveMonthlyBtn" onclick="toggleDonationType('monthly')" class="flex-1 py-3 bg-white text-black border-l font-bold transition-colors">
                    Give Monthly
                </button>
            </div>

            <p class="font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">Select donation amount (₹)</p>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-6">
                <button type="button" onclick="setAmount(5000, this)" class="amt-btn border border-gray-300 py-2.5 rounded hover:border-[#4caf50] hover:bg-green-50 transition-all">₹5000</button>
                <button type="button" onclick="setAmount(2500, this)" class="amt-btn border border-gray-300 py-2.5 rounded hover:border-[#4caf50] hover:bg-green-50 transition-all">₹2500</button>
                <button type="button" onclick="setAmount(2000, this)" class="amt-btn border border-gray-300 py-2.5 rounded hover:border-[#4caf50] hover:bg-green-50 transition-all">₹2000</button>
                <button type="button" onclick="setAmount(1500, this)" class="amt-btn border border-gray-300 py-2.5 rounded hover:border-[#4caf50] hover:bg-green-50 transition-all">₹1500</button>
                <button type="button" onclick="setAmount(1000, this)" class="amt-btn border border-gray-300 py-2.5 rounded hover:border-[#4caf50] hover:bg-green-50 transition-all">₹1000</button>
                <button type="button" onclick="setAmount(500, this)" class="amt-btn border border-gray-300 py-2.5 rounded hover:border-[#4caf50] hover:bg-green-50 transition-all">₹500</button>
            </div>

            <div class="relative mb-6">
                <span class="absolute left-3 top-2 text-gray-400">₹</span>
                <input type="text" id="customAmount" inputmode="numeric" pattern="[0-9]*" oninput="handleInput(this.value)" class="w-full border border-gray-300 pl-8 p-2.5 rounded focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500 outline-none" placeholder="Other Amount">
            </div>

            <p class="text-center mb-6 bg-green-50 py-2 rounded-lg">
                You pledge to serve <strong id="mealCount" class="text-green-600 text-lg">0</strong> nutritious meals<span id="mealFrequencyText"></span>.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                <button type="button" onclick="openDonorModal()" class="w-full bg-[#4caf50] hover:bg-[#43a047] text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-lg transition shadow-lg active:scale-95">
                    Proceed to Donate
       
                </button>
                <button type="button" onclick="openShareModal()" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border-2 border-gray-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50 font-bold py-3 rounded-lg transition">
